skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my joker
des:
It has a collection of the jokes as well as the pick up lines. 

You can say the following phrase to activate the skill.

 - Alexa, open my joker

If you would like to listen to the jokes, you could say one of the following phrases

- Alexa, ask my joker to tell a joke
- Alexa, open my joker for a joke
- Alexa, ask my joker to tell a joke

If you would like to listen to the pick up lines, you could say one of the following phrases

- Alexa, ask my joker to tell a pick up line
- Alexa, open my joker for a pick up line
- Alexa, ask my joker to tell a pick up line
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
